The average person dreams of having a rich partner and if as a girl, your partner is a billionaire, then it’s not a bad deal right? However, actress Keke Palmer had a back and forth with media personality and host, Steve Harvey during an appearance on his show, “Steve TV Show”. During the show, Harvey wants to make Palmer the wife of a billionaire according to her and they have a back-and-forth with her “uncle” about his insistence that she ties her fallopian tubes to a man worth nine figures. Watch the interesting video below: 